<body>
    <h2 class="center-align"> Signing up is Free! </h2>
    <div class="row center-align">
    <div class="row col s12 m6 ">
            <div class="card white center-align ">
                <div class="card-content black-text">
                    <div class="row">
                        <form class="col s12">
                            <div class="row">
                                <div class="input-field col s6">
                                    <input placeholder="First Name" id="first_name" type="text" class="validate">
                                    <label for="first_name"></label>
                                </div>
                                <div class="input-field col s6">
                                    <input placeholder="Last Name" id="last_name" type="text" class="validate">
                                    <label for="last_name"></label>
                                </div>
                                <div class="input-field col s6">
                                    <input placeholder="Username" id="userName" type="text" class="validate" data-length="15">
                                    <label for="user_name"></label>
                                  </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="row">
                                <div class="input-field col s12">
                                    <input placeholder="Password" id="password" type="password" class="validate">
                                    <label for="password"></label>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="row">
                                <div class="input-field col s12">
                                    <input placeholder="email" id="email" type="email" class="validate">
                                    <label for="email"></label>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <a class="waves-effect waves-light btn center-align">login</a>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col s6">
        <div class="therapyCard">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col s12 m7">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-image right-align">
                        <img src="/assets/images/familyTherapy.jpg">
                        <span class="card-title"></span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <p>Creating an account with us will provide you with resources to benefit you and your family. Signing up will allow you to utilize our Journal, Therapy Maps, and Health Tracker. It is free and confidential! Seek the help that you need whenever you need </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
